query_room_size_array

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_room_size_array -  This method returns the size of the room as a three element array always.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int * query_room_size_array()
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the size of the room as a three element array.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/basic_room.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the size of the room as a three element array always.


({ north-south size, east-west size, up-down size }) 

The sizes are all radii's so they are half the actual width of the room.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_room_size(), set_room_size()

.EP

